\s1 Preface
\p This publication includes the New Testament and Psalms in the Yopno language. There are approximately 9,000 Yopno speakers. The majority of them live in villages along the Yopno river and its tributaries in the Finisterre Mountains in both Morobe and Madang provinces of Papua New Guinea. Others live in various towns, especially Lae and Madang.
\p Lutheran evangelists, who came to bring God‚Äôs Word to the Yopno people in the 1920‚Äôs, told of a star that guided them to where they should begin telling the Good News. In a dream God told them to go to GuŇčam, an area named for a fern that grows there. And so the cover features, along with the cross and an open Bible, a star and two guŇčam plants, reminding the Yopno people of how Christianity came to the Yopno valley.
\p We offer thanks to God who out of love for the Yopno people determined to give them this special gift. We are grateful to Him for the many, many individuals who, by their faithfulness in prayer and giving over many years, have enabled us to complete this work. Through them, and many of our Yopno brothers and sisters in Christ, God has caused this portion of His Word to become a reality for the Yopno people in their own heart language.
\p We dedicate this book to God for His eternal glory. May He use the reading and teaching of this Book of Life to continue building His church among the Yopno people, both in numbers and in quality of faith.
\s1 But P…®so Gen
\p On papia uŇčun Yopno am…®n da iy…® da genonsi da PiŇčkop dakon gen bam…®si nandaŇč p…®saŇček PiŇčkop dakon galaktok yolek eg…®pni do wasaŇčbi.
\p PiŇčkop gen niaŇčon da apgut uŇčun dakon t…®lakni g…®pm…®kon tosok. G…®k da kosit yol…®Ňčakwan yabekbi mib…®ltoksi apgwit da uŇčun kaŇček yolek apgwit. PiŇčkop da geni kokup k…®nda mani GuŇčam uŇčudon aŇčk…®ni yaŇč d…®pm…®non yoy…®Ňčban nandaŇčakwa g…®k da mib…®ltaŇč yoban ab…®Ňč Isan aŇčalon awit. G…®k uŇčun sig…®n taŇčakwan Kumbul p…®Ňček GuŇčam m…®kt…®m kaŇčakwa g…®k uŇčun pas…®lg…®t. AŇčakwan uŇčudon kokup wasaŇček PiŇčkop gen K√Ęte genon da wasaŇček yoy…®wit. Lutheran dakon pi am…®n da b…®lak morapm…®si pi madepsi awit da aŇč uŇčun do ya yaŇčsi yoyamaŇč.
\p Ae don SIL da paŇčpulugaŇček Yopno genonsi da PiŇčkop gen paŇčtob…®l nimgwit. Ae uŇčun g…®n d…®ma, Yopno gen papia yut k…®si wasawit, aŇček yoy…®Ňčdet paŇčtagap awit da yoy…®Ňčdet aŇč. UŇčun do ya yaŇčsi yoyamaŇč.
\p PiŇčkop da Yopno am…®n do butdasi galaktaŇč yom…®Ňček geni pakyaŇčsi nandaŇč p…®soneŇč do si nand…®sak. Gen d…®war…®kon da k…®l…® apgut, mani nin da genonsi da bam…®si ab…®daŇček Yesu butdasi yol k…®motneŇč do tag…®si nand…®sak.
\p Do not, papia on butdasi ab…®daŇček b…®sapm…® b…®sapm…® manj…®Ňčaki PiŇčkop gen da gak aŇčpulugaŇčban on m…®kt…®mon j…®g…® morap noman taŇč gamni b…®sapmon tebai agek, don eg…®p eg…®p teban ab…®doki. 
